Notes:

# For applying Security using Authorization

1. Enable Web security in Security Configuration file
@EnableWebSecurity

2. Extends to WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter

3. Override configure(AuthenticationManagerBuilder auth)
- It accepts username, password & authorities

4. Override configure(HttpSecurity http)
- specify pattern with roles

4. Create @Bean for PasswordEncoder 



# For BYPASSING url

1. Add antPattern where .permitAll is called